The paper deals with the construction and analysis of linear codes, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The paper also discusses the security of codes, which is a topic in cryptography (cs.CR) and coding theory (cs.CC). Finally, the paper presents a new method for constructing minimal linear codes, which involves solving optimization problems, a topic in numerical analysis (cs.NA).
